se.soprasteria.automatedtesting.webdriver.api.base

Class BasePageObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • se.soprasteria.automatedtesting.webdriver.api.base.BaseClass
      • se.soprasteria.automatedtesting.webdriver.api.base.BasePageObject
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AddLocationAndroid, AddLocationIOS, AddLocationWeb, AddPopularPlacesAndroid, APIBasePageObject, DailyNotificationsAndroid, LoginPageWeb, MainPageAndroid, MainPageIOS, MainPageWeb, MainPageWeb, SidemenuAndroid

    public abstract class BasePageObject
extends BaseClass
    Base pageobject to extend when creating pageobjects. Initializes a logger and ensures the existence of the isPageLoaded() state and action. Also houses elementHelper that has functions to streamline working with selenium webelements and driverhelpers that streamline working with selenium webdrivers. Page objects is a designpattern used by us to basically wrap all the technical functionality to interact with the page behind functions that are easier to understand.
